      <div class="bg-[#8794ba] text-white p-10 md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center items-start">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 font-title">Welcome Back!</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Practice now and turn <br />
